      <display_string>[Article] Tangherlini, Timothy R. 2000. "How do you know she's a witch"? : Witches, cunning folk, and competition in Denmark. Vol. 59 of &lt;i&gt;Western Folklore&lt;/i&gt; 3-4: 279-303.</display_string>
